790
00:36:33,539 --> 00:36:37,151
- Alexa...I hear you,

791
00:36:37,195 --> 00:36:41,242
but we gotta focus
on right now, okay?

792
00:36:41,286 --> 00:36:44,158
I'm willing
to work with you, okay?

793
00:36:44,202 --> 00:36:46,552
But we gotta build trust.
The best way to do that

794
00:36:46,595 --> 00:36:48,293
is to let Karla go.

795
