819
00:37:53,445 --> 00:37:55,185
- Alexa didn't make it.

820
00:37:55,229 --> 00:37:57,318
- Get the knife
to the Crime Lab.

821
00:37:57,362 --> 00:37:58,319
- Yeah, it's on its way.

822
00:37:58,363 --> 00:37:59,886
What do you
wanna do with Karla?

